{"word":"G5141 - τρέμω - trémō - trem'-o - Be afraid","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τρέμω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">trémō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">trem'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be afraid</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நடுங்கு, அஞ்சியிரு"},{"paragraph":"to tremble"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Strengthened from a primary word <b>&#x03C4;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>treo&#x0304;</b> (to &ldquo;dread&rdquo;, &ldquo;terrify&rdquo;); to &ldquo;tremble&rdquo; or <i>fear:</i> - be afraid, trembling.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}